### Get cart for user
GET https://localhost:7000/api/cart/user123

### Add item to cart (depends on existing product)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/cart/user123/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### Add another item to cart
POST https://localhost:7000/api/cart/user123/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 2,
  "quantity": 1
}

### Add same product again (should increase quantity)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/cart/user123/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 1
}

### Get updated cart
GET https://localhost:7000/api/cart/user123

### Remove specific item from cart
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/cart/user123/items/2

### Get cart after removal
GET https://localhost:7000/api/cart/user123

### Clear entire cart
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/cart/user123

### Try to get empty cart
GET https://localhost:7000/api/cart/user123

